    "## SDR Signal Analysis: Foundation\n",
    "### Power Spectral Density (PSD) and Spectral Correlation Density (SCD)\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook contains the foundational analysis plots: the PSD and the self-contained SCD."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
